%form#PopUpTumor.PopUp
	
	/ HEADER
	
	%header
		%input#ButtonCancel.ButtonPrimary.PositionerLeft{ :type => "button", :value => "Cancel", :onclick => "buttonSubPopUpCancel('PopUpTumor', 'PopUpCell')" }
		%input#ButtonDone.ButtonPrimary.PositionerRight{ :type => "button", :value => "Done", :onclick => "buttonSubPopUpDone('PopUpTumor', 'PopUpCell', stringPageInfixTypeCurrent + 'Tumor', arrayHealthQuestionnaire)" }
		%h2 Kuesioner Tumor

	/ FIELDSET

	%fieldset
		%div.ContainerFit
			%span.Multi.Single.6l Gangguan fungsi Pertumbuhan Sel, Tumor, Kista, Kanker, Benjolan pada permukaan kulit atau pertumbuhan abnormal lainnya?
		%br
		%hr

		%label.medium.Single.Item 1. Kapan pertama kali diketahui adanya tumor?
		%br    
		%input#DateProspectiveInsuredTumorFirstTime.Full.Multi.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text", "data-field" => "date" }
		%br
		%hr

		%label.medium.Single.Item 2. Pada bagian tubuh mana tumor tersebut tumbuh?
		%br    
		%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorWhere.Full.Multi.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
		%br
		%hr

		%label.medium.Single.Item 3. Bila diketahui sebutkan diagnosis pasti dari tumor tersebut.
		%br    
		%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorDiagnose.Full.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
		%br
		%hr

		%label#Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft 4. Apakah tumor tersebut telah diangkat/ dioperasi?
		%div.RadioButton.Medium.PositionerRight
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTakenYes{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTaken", :value => "ya" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTakenYes" } Ya
			%div.Separator
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTakenNo{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTaken", :value => "tidak" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTakenNo" } Tidak
		%br

		%div.ContainerFit
			%label#LabelProspectiveInsuredTumorOperation.Long.Single.Item a. Tanggal operasi
			%input#DateProspectiveInsuredTumorOperation.Full.Single.Item{ :type =>"text" }
		%br

		%label.medium.Single.Item b. Metode operasi (anestesi local, bedah beku/cryosurgery, operasi dengan anestesi umum, dan sebagainya). Mohon menjelaskan secara rinci pada kolom di bawah ini.

		%br    
		%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorMethod.Full.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
		%br

		%label.medium.Single.Item c. Mohon lengkapi data Dokter dan Rumah Sakit yang biasa dikunjungi untuk gangguan pernapasan.
		%br    
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Tanggal terakhir konsultasi
			%input#DateProspectiveInsuredTumorLast.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Nama Lengkap Dokter:
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorDoctName.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin No. Telepon/Handphone:
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorPhone.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Nama Klinik/Rumah Sakit:
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorClinic.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Alamat Klinik/Rumah Sakit:
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorAddress.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%br


		%label.medium.Single.Item d. Pengobatan/ tindakan apa yang diberikan setelah dilakukan operasi tumor (seperti minum obat tablet, radioterapi, kemotherapi, dan sebagainya) ?
		%br    
		%div.RadioButton.Medium.PositionerRight
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapyDrug{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapy", :value => "obattablet" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapyDrug" } Obat tablet
			%div.Separator
			
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapyRadio{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapy", :value => "radioterapi" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapyRadio" } Radioterapi
			%div.Separator
			
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapyKemo{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapy", :value => "kemoterapi" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapyKemo" } Kemoterapi
			%div.Separator
			
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapyOther{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapy", :value => "other" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapyOther" } Lainnya, Sebutkan.
			%div.Separator			
			%br
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorTherapyOther.Line.Long.Single.PositionerLeft{ :type => "text" }
		%br

		%label#Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft e. Apakah anda pernah diberi informasi tentang prognosa (ramalan) atas tumor tersebut?
		%div.RadioButton.Medium.PositionerRight
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorPrognosaYes{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorPrognosa", :value => "ya" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorPrognosaYes" } Ya
			%div.Separator
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorPrognosaNo{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorPrognosa", :value => "tidak" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorPrognosaNo" } Tidak
		%br    
			%label.Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft{ :for => "TextProspectiveInsuredTumorPrognosa"}
			Mohon menjelaskan secara rinci pada kolom di bawah ini.
			%br
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorPrognosa.Line.Long.Single.PositionerLeft{ :type => "text" }
		%br

		%label.medium.Single.Item f. Pemeriksaan-pemeriksaan apa saja yang telah dilakukan, termasuk tanggal dan hasil pemeriksaan tersebut.
		%br
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Center.Margin Jenis Pemeriksaan
			%label.Short.Single.Item1.Center.Margin Tanggal Pemeriksaan
			%label.Short.Single.Item1.Center.Margin Hasil Pemeriksaan
			%a.NavigationPopUp{ :href => "#" } 
		%div.ContainerFit
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupType1.Short.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupDate1.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupResult1.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupType2.Short.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupDate2.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupResult2.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupType3.Short.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupDate3.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupResult3.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupType4.Short.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupDate4.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TableProspectiveInsuredTumorCheckupResult4.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }			
		%br
		%label.medium.Single.Item g. Pengobatan atau tindakan operasi apa saja yang pernah dianjurkan?
		%br    
		%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorActionDesc.Full.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
		%br
		%hr

		%label#Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft 5. Apakah sampai saat ini masih dalam pengobatan?
		%div.RadioButton.Medium.PositionerRight
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorCurrentYes{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorCurrent", :value => "ya" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorCurrentYes" } Ya
			%div.Separator
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorCurrentNo{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorCurrent", :value => "tidak" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorCurrentNo" } Tidak
		%br
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Tanggal terakhir perawatan:
			%input#DateProspectiveInsuredTumorLastTherapy.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Alasan
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorReason.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Pengobatan
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorTreatment.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Berapa kali dalam 1 tahun
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorHowOften.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Nama Lengkap Dokter
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorDocterName.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin No. Telepon/Handphone:
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorTelephone.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Nama Klinik/Rumah Sakit:
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorClinicName.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }	
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Margin Alamat Klinik/Rumah Sakit:
			%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorClinicAddrs.Long.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }				
		%br
		%label.medium.Single.Item Sejak kapan Anda tidak lagi dalam perawatan lanjutan?
		%br    
		%input#TextPolicyHolderSejakKapanTidakLagiPerawatan.Full.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
		%br
		%hr

		%label#Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft 6. Apakah anda pernah tidak masuk kerja karena gangguan ini?  
		%div.RadioButton.Medium.PositionerRight
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorLeaveYes{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorLeave", :value => "ya" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorLeaveYes" } Ya
			%div.Separator
			%input#RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorLeaveNo{ :type => "radio", :name => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorLeave", :value => "ya" }
			%label.RadioButton{ :for => "RadioButtonProspectiveInsuredTumorLeaveNo" } Tidak
			%br
			%label#Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft Jika “Ya”, kapan:
		%br    
		%input#DateProspectiveInsuredTumorLeave.Full.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
		%br    
		%label#Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft dan berapa lama?:
		%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorHowLong.Full.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
		%br
		%label#Wrap.Single.PositionerLeft hari
		%hr

		%label.medium.Single.Item 7. Sebutkan kapan terakhir kali Anda melakukan konsultasi dengan dokter? Mohon tuliskan tanggal konsultasi, pemeriksaan yang dilakukan dan hasilnya.
		%div.ContainerFit
			%label.Short.Single.Item.Center.Margin Jenis Pemeriksaan
			%label.Short.Single.Item1.Center.Margin Tanggal Pemeriksaan
			%label.Short.Single.Item1.Center.Margin Hasil Pemeriksaan
		%div.ContainerFit
			%input#TextPolicyHolderJenisPemeriksaan1.Short.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TextPolicyHolderTanggalPemeriksaan1.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TextPolicyHolderHasilPemeriksaan1.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%input#TextPolicyHolderJenisPemeriksaan2.Short.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TextPolicyHolderTanggalPemeriksaan2.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TextPolicyHolderHasilPemeriksaan12.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%div.ContainerFit
			%input#TextPolicyHolderJenisPemeriksaan3.Short.Single.Item.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TextPolicyHolderTanggalPemeriksaan3.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
			%input#TextPolicyHolderHasilPemeriksaan13.Short.Single.Item1.Margin{ :type => "text" }
		%br
		%hr

		%label.medium.Single.Item 8. Mohon sebutkan bila ada informasi lain sehubungan dengan kondisi kesehatan anda yang mungkin dapat membantu proses pengajuan Asuransi ini.
		%br    
		%input#TextProspectiveInsuredTumorAdditionalInfo.Full.Multi.Item1.Margin{ :type =>"text" }
		%br
		%hr

